channel.description:
WelCome To UniqueScape V1 - Im First Time Poster, I Been Codeing This Server For 8 Months
Credits:70% For Making Server/Client :10% To WinterLove For Server Base :10% To Client Maker :10& To MorparScape TUTS
Server: WinterLove For ServerBase, Client: Cant Rember, [Made Own Custom Icons]
I Will Post Alot Of Pictures Of My Server, And Some Pictures Are Good, Theres Some Parts On The Server I Aint Added Pictures To,
Please Follow What I Have Said when You Need To Add characters,moreinfo,connectedfrom - Because If You Dont You Wont Be Able To PLAY SERVER.
Skills: Attack [100%] Defence [100%] Strenth [100%] Hitpoints [100%] Range [100%] Prayer [100%] Magic [100%] Cooking [100%] WoodCutting [100%] Fletching [100%] Fishing [100%] FireMaking [100%] Crafting [100%] Smithing [80%] [Need Some Bits Sorting Out] Mining [100%] Herblore [100%] Agility [0%] [Making So CrystalBow/Crystal Shield Trains Agility] Thieving [100%] Slayer [100%] Farming [100%] RuneCraft [100%]
I Have Got Fully working Slayer With Tasks To Do, I Have Got Fully Own Made Quests, I Have Got SkillCapes [Made SkillCape Master Talk To Them For SkillCape When You got 99 Skill] I Have Got Fully Working Barrows I Have Got Fully Working Jad MiniGame I Have Got Fully Working Fight Pits
